, "lines": ["えーアカンの？"]}, {"box": [974, 587, 1001, 675], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27, "lines_coords": [[[974.0, 587.0], [1001.0, 587.0], [1001.0, 675.0], [974.0, 675.0]]], "lines": ["チューブのやつは西洋わさびとか"]}, {"box": [954, 789, 1003, 913], "vertical": true, "font_size": 49, "lines_coords": [[[954.0, 789.0], [1003.0, 789.0], [1003.0, 913.0], [954.0, 913.0]]], "lines": ["そっちのアイスは冷蔵庫置いといて少しずつ自分で片付けるん"]}, {"box": [821, 584, 845, 710], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24, "lines_coords": [[[821.0, 584.0], [845.0, 584.0], [845.0, 710.0], [821.0, 710.0]]], "lines": ["添加物とか混ざっとるから別モンらしいで"]}, {"box": [647, 510, 701, 554], "vertical": false, "font_size": 44, "lines_coords": [[[647.0, 510.0], [701.0, 510.0], [701.0, 554.0], [647.0, 554.0]]], "lines": ["んの"]}, {"box": [647, 511, 701, 554], "vertical": false, "font_size": 47, "lines_coords": [[[647.0, 507.0], [701.0, 507.0], [701.0, 558.0], [647.0, 558.0]]], "lines": ["ん？"]}, {"box": [781, 689, 797, 738], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16, "lines_coords": [[[781.0, 689.0], [797.0, 689.0], [797.0, 738.0], [781.0, 738.0]]], "lines": ["えー"]}, {"box": [790, 820, 828, 918], "vertical": true, "font_size": 38, "lines_coords": [[[790.0, 820.0], [828.0, 820.0], [828.0, 918.0], [790.0, 918.0]]], "lines": ["えーあおいちゃんも手伝ってーな"]}, {"box": [641, 607, 702, 997], "vertical": true, "font_size": 56, "lines_coords": [[[645.0, 609.0], [701.0, 609.0], [697.0, 997.0], [641.0, 997.0]]], "lines": ["ゆるキ；Ｊ△："]}, {"box": [266, 788, 298, 872], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32, "lines_coords": [[[266.0, 788.0], [298.0, 788.0], [298.0, 872.0], [266.0, 872.0]]], "lines": ["あかり何食べとるん"]}, {"box": [1247, 984, 1262, 1051], "vertical": true, "font_size": 15, "lines_coords": [[[1247.0, 984.0], [1262.0, 984.0], [1262.0, 1051.0], [1247.0, 1051.0]]], "lines": ["うまっ！！"]}, {"box": [1237, 1169, 1272, 1310], "vertical": true, "font_size": 35, "lines_coords": [[[1237.0, 1169.0], [1272.0, 1169.0], [1272.0, 1310.0], [1237.0, 1310.0]]], "lines": ["でもあおいちゃん作ってもうたこっちのやつどうしよ？"]}, {"